Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:05.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Great weather, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How about we ditch the supplementary classes and go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:15.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, you say things like that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:18.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Think about it. I don't have\Nany intention of going to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All this exam preparation is meaningless to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:24.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even so, you have to follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It will affect the recommendation the school writes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:29.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're really worried about me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since you're… uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…a very important person to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, how may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can we hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:48.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:53.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, um… someone might see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:55.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone around, so don't worry. {ep 22 little change}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:59.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're dating, so what's wrong with us holding hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:03.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I guess. Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:08.69,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:09.98,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:13.79,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're both looking rather hot this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:16.78,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What? Were you two about to kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:18.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We wouldn't do that, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:22.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, we were just going to hold han—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:05.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,After the School Festival and exams ended, summer break started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:10.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm still staying at Nagisa's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:16.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even though it's summer break,\Nthe seniors have supplementary class every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:21.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,With Nagisa around, I can't skip out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.38,Default-alt,Teacher,0,0,0,,Did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:26.38,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Extra Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:26.38,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}What Happened Over Summer Break
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:32.59,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,These daily supplementary classes are making me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:37.70,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,We only get one summer break as a senior,\Nand it's totally being stained gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:42.54,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I enjoy studying with everyone in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:46.14,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,And we can all eat our bentos together like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.53,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If I may ask, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.88,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I had to come to take care of Student Council related work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.29,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:58.26,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm asking why you are here in this room when you're not in the Theater Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.30,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What happened to Okazaki today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:05.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I heard that Okazaki-san will be going over to Sunohara-san's today. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I-Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:12.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You still call him “Okazaki-san”, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, is there something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:19.29,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun is calling you “Nagisa”.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.66,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Since you're dating, it wouldn't hurt\Nto call each other by name, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It feels like someone said the same thing here in this room before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.26,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Also, how far have you two gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Well, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.34,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Huh?! Still haven't even held hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.12,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot? {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What have you been doing for all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:47.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Shut up. You get nervous when the opportunity comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan should forget about someone who's got no balls…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:55.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,…and notice my platonic love for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.96,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sunohara, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:04:59.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.31,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,A really cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.75,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,She said she wants to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.19,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:13.68,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:19.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.60,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:29.57,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I told you over the phone that I'd come visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.68,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.95,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You're so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:39.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Once we finish cleaning here,\Nlet's go see the old man and Sanae-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:39.91,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.55,Default,All,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:53.13,San,San,0,0,0,,You're a well-behaved girl as always, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:56.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's seriously hard to believe that you're Sunohara's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:00.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say that.\NSunohara-san is a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:04.10,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So, you'll be staying with us this time, too, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.07,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.97,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Damn right. Stay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:12.47,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Go get in the bath with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.52,San,San,0,0,0,,I'll join in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This family loves guests as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's a little cramped, but please bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:23.28,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:26.56,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,The more cramped it is, the closer I get to be to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.44,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Looks like fun…{ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:26.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could join in. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.77,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Good morning, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Morning. You didn't get enough sleep last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.36,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's because we were talking until late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.90,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Mostly about Okazaki-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What exactly did they say about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.83,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Nagisa-san, how about getting some more sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:07:00.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine. Besides, I don't have\Nsupplementary classes to worry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you help out with the store, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:09.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, since I want Dad and Mom\Nto have some time off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.46,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm happy to be able to be of help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:18.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Though, it's a shame that I can't go out with you despite it being during break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Work hard for my sake, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:27.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's free time my daughter made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:28.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Of course…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.36,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,…I'll play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:31.98,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:36.79,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It must be nice to never lose the heart of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.39,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I took so much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.67,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Did you bake that bread, Sanae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:45.44,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.27,San,San,0,0,0,,Would you try one for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:49.50,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:55.85,San,San,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.08,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes, they looked very delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.37,San,San,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:02.17,San,San,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll get sold out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:04.02,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Never thought of getting out of it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. It was very educational.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:10.94,San,San,0,0,0,,I have a gathering to go to as well, so I'll leave the place to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.65,Default-alt,Car,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.47,Default-alt,Car,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is the junk collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:26.52,Default-alt,Car,0,0,0,,{\an8}If there are any televisions, refrigerators, computers, motor bikes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.42,Default-alt,Car,0,0,0,,{\an8}and other machines no longer in use sitting in your house, please feel free to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's really boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:32.25,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I remember seeing more customers last time I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:36.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This time of the year is when students are away from school, so sales always go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.40,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.04,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.10,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:42.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What a fast reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.35,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:47.81,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,We have very cute girls watching the store today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.96,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes, Nagisa-san is very cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She's talking about Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.52,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,No, I'm talking about both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:58.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.28,Default,3,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:06.40,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san wasn't being of any use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Three people here is more than you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, I'm not needed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:17.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm very happy to be with Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.82,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, how about you try working the cash register.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:23.01,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'll go out to call in customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,“Call in”?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey! Mei—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:26.99,Default,2,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.72,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,Oh, no Sanae-san or Akio-san today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. We're watching the store today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.66,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,Oh, this is a bakery?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:42.00,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,Oh. I knew it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.07,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,Like, the outside is totally a normal shop's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.73,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,The bread here is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.42,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,In that case, I guess I'll buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.23,Default,2,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.21,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,Hey, this is a bakery!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.19,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.49,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,But look, the girl in here is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Take care of the register!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:09.72,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:13.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you saying to call customers in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.11,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,“We've got cute girls!”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're making it sound like we're some shady shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.38,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'll reel customers in like it's a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:22.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Could you help inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.42,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,We've got cute girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.05,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Would you like to stop by?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.88,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What? This place was a bakery?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.14,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,So what if it is? The girls outside and inside are both cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:43.76,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I don't think we've sold this much since this store's opening day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Try working a little bit more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:52.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We had people coming back, sometimes up to three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even all of Sanae-san's bread got sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the biggest surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:11:01.02,San,San,0,0,0,,You speak as though it's expected for my bread to not sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.53,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:06.20,San,San,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. I love you very much, too, Akio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.56,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Why don't you say it, too, Okazaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.95,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Nagisa, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:16.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I-I can't say that, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:19.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I-I'll go prepare the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm going to go sweep outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:31.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So she's out playing with Nagisa-chan today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:40.21,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What could she be doing that's worth abandoning her brother like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:42.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't be depressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:44.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll stop by here at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.27,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.95,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,See, she did come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.37,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Ah fine. I guess I'll deal with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's so easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.84,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I knew I'd find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:11:59.75,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:05.32,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, I want to have a private conversation with Okazaki-san, so can you go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:10.50,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Come on! You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.88,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:18.81,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:23.93,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I know this is sudden, but I decided to become the cupid of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,“Cupid of love”?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:25.98,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:30.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see, so you were worried, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I don't see a suitable partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:36.04,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:37.95,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,There's one right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara and Mei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,An incestuous relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.20,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You know, Onii-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:53.12,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,After you went far away, I started to think of you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Really? How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:13:00.08,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Things I'd never even thought about while you were around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.39,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Do you look up to me a little now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.02,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,No, not exactly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:06.78,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,In a more…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:08.65,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,…naughty way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Mei…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're such a naughty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.10,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Holy shit! I'm getting turned on! {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.53,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Could you not start letting your imagination run wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But you and Sunohara, right?\NHow could I not get turned on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:28.67,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Please don't imagine such a terrifying thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:31.80,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Besides, I said I'm the cupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wait, then you're here for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.42,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know, Sunohara…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.40,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Okazaki? {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:45.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I've been starting to think about you a lot these days. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.50,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Really? How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:51.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Things I'd never even thought about while around other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Have I become a best friend\Nthat you can be a little proud of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, not exactly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:57.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,More like…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:03.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,More like, I want to wear matching boxers with you as you run down the road to school…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.01,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Tomoya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on, catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.98,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, don't play with me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I said over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:14.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Holy shit… That turns me off…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:21.87,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You're not letting me make any progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:25.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. The old man's character could be infecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:29.08,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What I'm talking about is Okazaki-san and Nagisa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:30.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:33.67,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Frankly, you two aren't being honest with each other yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:37.50,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's been weeks since you\Nstarted dating, so this is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:41.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why must I hear this from a girl in junior high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:47.02,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I have a question. How would you like Nagisa-san to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,“How?” you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:55.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She has the tendency to think negatively of herself, so I'd like her to have more confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.99,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,That's the same way I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.47,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,This is great. It'll probably work well if this is the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:01.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Work well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:01.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, Okazaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.28,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Oh my, speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.97,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.31,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.92,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,So excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:20.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Weren't you playing with her until a bit ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:25.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I was. I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Huh? “Tomoya-kun”?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, do you have some free time right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:36.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm totally free…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:40.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's good. Then let's go for a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:46.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, it's just that I felt like walking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Was it too much to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:49.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:54.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um… T… Tomoya-kun, you're super lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:16:00.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since you're walking with a slightly cute girl like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:06.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um… Even though I say “cute”, it's only “slightly”.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay… So where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:12.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are we heading home right off the bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:18.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If I don't, the plan won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:19.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Nothing! That was idle talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:25.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What? It's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:31.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why would you say, “Hello”, when you've returned to your own house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Because I'm here as a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll buy some bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:36.64,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't bother. Just take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.89,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Since we're bound to have leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That'd be cheating. I will pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:45.77,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Fine, fine. I know how stubborn you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.16,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:48.58,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.67,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't step on the landmine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What do you mean by “landmine”?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, brat. Enlighten her. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.67,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around! I know you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:00.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:07.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You leave me no choice.\NI'll spell everything out for you, then. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,When I say landmine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.72,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,it's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,…Sanae's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:15.27,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,…bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.14,San,San,0,0,0,,So my bread was…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.61,San,San,0,0,0,,…Furukawa Bread's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:21.14,San,San,0,0,0,,…landmine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:25.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:27.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So what are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:31.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Anyway, I will pay properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:38.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, can I ask you to pay for this, Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't have cash on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:44.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I do, but I want you to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:46.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, you can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't mind. How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,¥120.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:51.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm making Tomoya-kun pay for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:18:00.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How can you say that after asking me to pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:03.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, I'm sure you're not upset about it or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Because…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…the one you paid for was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can you say that one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather not if I can help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But, I couldn't hear you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:21.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Really? Then I'll have to say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:26.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I was the one you paid for, so I'm sure you're not upset about it or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Did you hear me clearly this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Really? Then I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:46.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous, I can't taste anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:50.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,N-No! I didn't mean to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:51.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's Oka—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's Tomoya-kun's treat, so it's better than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:56.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd like a bite, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't want you speaking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then I'll change it to a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Would you like a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you need me to say, “Yes, I want a bite”?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you want a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd really like a bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:19.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Well I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Because there's only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, you must have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:35.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll have you enjoy it in a different manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:39.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then, please look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:41.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:42.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, how was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sure you smelled the cinnamon roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:05.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um… If you don't say something, I'll feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey! Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I knew you set all this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.39,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,So you had it figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:16.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is too unnatural no matter how you look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.00,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,The date ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.55,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:26.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That brat…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:33.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Does Mei-chan have dirt on you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.38,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that. Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did she say something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:45.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She said, “Because Okazaki-san is a delinquent, he can't force himself to be proactive.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:49.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She also said that I should take\Nthe lead since I'm the older one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:52.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I figured it was something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:57.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I acted as Mei-chan planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:01.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I must have seemed strange, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:02.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:07.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you not like me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How would I not like you because of something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:15.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Plus, what Mei-chan said probably isn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you still have some time, Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:23.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,There's still some time left before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay. Then I guess we can still go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.99,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Anywhere would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,As long as I'm with Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:46.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll always be with you.
